<p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 15px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: black !important">近日，由中国建筑装饰协会（国家一级协会）、江西省生产力学会、江西省陈设艺术协会联合主办，江西软件职业技术大学承办的《第四届江西高校空间设计大赛（美华杯）》获奖名单揭晓。我校VR与艺术学院师生在本次大赛中获得优秀组织奖1个、优秀指导老师奖1个、个人获奖90个。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 15px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: black !important"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/2023-04-27%2021%3A40%3A50%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%871.png?Expires=1997962850&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=22YsFLayc0OTO4dX%2FihIXxyPVsc%3D" alt="" width="650" height="497" style="box-sizing: border-box;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;padding: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;filter: saturate(1.1);display: block"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: bord